title: Dobhan
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Indian, Take-out, Nepalese, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Modern take on Indian and Nepali cuisine with one menu page devoted to vegan/vegetarian food including edamame, steamed greens in sesame dressing, coconut-crusted tofu, couscous tagine, seitan, and brown rice. Bright atmosphere with colorful decor, in the Schenk-Atwood neighborhood.
